statements.sql: select `t_booking`.*, `t1`.`p_no`, `t1`.`p_name`, `t2`.`clinic_name`, `t3`.`facility_name`, `t4`.`equipment_name`, `t5`.`inspection_name`, `t6`.`insurance_name` from `t_booking` left join `t_patient` as `t1` on `t_booking`.`patient_id` = `t1`.`p_id` left join `m_clinic` as `t2` on `t_booking`.`clinic_id` = `t2`.`clinic_id` left join `t_facility` as `t3` on `t_booking`.`facility_id` = `t3`.`facility_id` left join `m_equipment` as `t4` on `t_booking`.`equipment_id` = `t4`.`equipment_id` left join `m_inspection` as `t5` on `t_booking`.`inspection_id` = `t5`.`inspection_id` left join `m_insurance` as `t6` on `t_booking`.`insurance_id` = `t6`.`insurance_id` where `booking_id` is null limit 1
